# Iterable - Protocol for types that can be iterated over in for-in loops
module Core

### Defines the protocol `Iterable`.
### :typeparam T: The value used for `T`.
protocol Iterable[T]
  ### Creates an iterator for this value.
  ### :returns: The resulting `Iterator[T]` value.
  @readonly
  routine Me.$iter() -> Iterator[T]
